---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="域名输入错误｜即将跳转">
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="card" role="alert" aria-live="polite">
      <div class="badge">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        域名输入错误提示
      </div>

      <h1>你来到了错误的网站：<span class="count" id="currentHost"></span></h1>

      <p>
        正确网站是：<strong>prts.wiki</strong>。你可能把它打成了 <strong>ptrs.wiki</strong>。
      </p>

      <div class="info">
        <p>
          正确网址：
          <span class="count" id="targetUrlText">https://prts.wiki/</span>
        </p>
        <p class="sr-only" id="announce"></p>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <a class="btn primary" id="goNow" href="https://prts.wiki/" rel="noopener noreferrer">立即跳转</a>
        <button class="btn" id="cancel" type="button">取消自动跳转</button>
        <a class="btn" id="copy" href="#" role="button">复制正确链接</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      这是一个提示页面，不提供任何内容服务。请以浏览器地址栏显示的域名为准。
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script>
    !function(){var a="https://prts.wiki/",b=document.getElementById("currentHost"),c=document.getElementById("goNow"),d=document.getElementById("cancel"),e=document.getElementById("copy"),f=document.getElementById("targetUrlText"),g=a.replace(/\/$/,"")+location.pathname+location.search+location.hash;b.textContent=location.host||"（未知）",c.href=g,f.textContent=g,d.addEventListener("click",function(){d.textContent="已取消自动跳转",d.disabled=!0}),e.addEventListener("click",async function(a){a.preventDefault();try{await navigator.clipboard.writeText(g),e.textContent="已复制",setTimeout(function(){e.textContent="复制正确链接"},1200)}catch(a){alert("复制失败，请手动复制链接：\n"+g)}})}();
  </script>
</Layout>
